title: Prego do Mar (Ilhéu do)
body:
It is also known by the names Ilhéu do Furilhão or better Farilhão and Ilhéu do Navio. It is located north of Ilhéu Chão, in the Desertas. It is a rock about 40 meters high and 8 in circumference, resembling a sailing ship from a distance, and from this circumstance it is called Ilhéu do Navio.

## See Furilhão.

Ilhéu Chão: Located south of Ilhéu do Navio, in the Desertas
